    "en": {
      "title": "Gota comes tomorrow: a special security program",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa is scheduled to visit the island tomorrow.",
        "The police say that a special security program will be implemented for the security of Mr. Rajapaksa who is coming to the island.",
        "Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa was scheduled to visit Sri Lanka last month, but his visit was delayed due to security reasons."
      ],
